metadata.name: Dolly The Sheep Society #1
metadata.description: The Cold War ended, yet the pressure between the East and the West was higher than ever. Scottish scientists worked day and night to create what seemed to be impossible – to clone an animal. After numerous failed attempts Dolly was created – the first cloned animal in the world. But beware, this high-advanced technology was stolen by an evil scientist, who had the desire to use it to create an army, but instead, he created 7500 more clones of Dolly, some of them rarer than others. The story does not end here, because Dolly and her clones are yet to experience all the adventures awaiting them…
